–1930, bilingual text, Russian and Italian, ed. intro. trans. from Russian by A. Ponzio. Milan: Bompiani.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Bachtin%2C%20Michail%20e%20il%20suo%20Circolo.%202014.%20Opere%201919%E2%80%931930%2C%20bilingual%20text%2C%20Russian%20and%20Italian%2C%20ed.%20intro.%20trans.%20from%20Russian%20by%20A.%20Ponzio.%20Milan%3A%20Bompiani." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0010_ref_009_w2aab2b8c24b1b7b1ab2ab9Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Benjamin, W. 1972a [1931]. Der destruktive Charakter, in Benjamin, Gesammelte Schriften, 1972, trad. it. Il carattere distruttivo, in Millepiani, 4, 1995, 9–12.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Benjamin%2C%20W.%201972a%20%5B1931%5D.%20Der%20destruktive%20Charakter%2C%20in%20Benjamin%2C%20Gesammelte%20Schriften%2C%201972%2C%20trad.%20it.%20Il%20carattere%20distruttivo%2C%20in%20Millepiani%2C%204%2C%201995%2C%209%E2%80%9312." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0010_ref_010_w2aab2b8c24b1b7b1ab2ac10Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Benjamin, W. 1972b [1933]. “Erfahrung und Armut”, in Benjamin, Gesammelte Schriften, 1972, trad. it. Esperienza e povertà, in Millepiani, 4, 1995, 15–21.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Benjamin%2C%20W.%201972b%20%5B1933%5D.%20%E2%80%9CErfahrung%20und%20Armut%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20Benjamin%2C%20Gesammelte%20Schriften%2C%201972%2C%20trad.%20it.%20Esperienza%20e%20povert%C3%A0%2C%20in%20Millepiani%2C%204%2C%201995%2C%2015%E2%80%9321." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_